references: Repealing: Ord 69372, Ord 69375, Ord 69385, Ord 69387, Ord 69401, Ord 69414, Ord 69417, Ord 69418, Ord 69437
summary: An ordinance relating to certain unpaid claims against the City in connection with its street railway system, and repealing Ordinances Nos. 69372, 69375, 69385, 69387, 69401, 69414, 69417, 69418 and 69437 providing for payment thereof out of the Railway Emergency Operating Fund.
